9 (B) CARRYING OUT HIGHLY FOCUSED, INNOVATIVE, LOCALLY DEVELOPED ACTIVITIES TO EXPAND OR
10 ENHANCE EXISTING LANGUAGE INSTRUCTION EDUCATIONAL PROGRAMS AND ACADEMIC CONTENT INSTRUCTIONAL
11 PROGRAMS; AND
12 (C) IMPLEMENTING SCHOOLWIDE PROGRAMS WITHIN AN INDIVIDUAL SCHOOL AND SYSTEMWIDE PROGRAMS
13 WITHIN A SCHOOL DISTRICT TO RESTRUCTURE, REFORM, AND UPGRADE PROGRAMS, ACTIVITIES, AND OPERATIONS
14 RELATED TO THE LANGUAGE INSTRUCTION EDUCATIONAL PROGRAMS AND ACADEMIC CONTENT INSTRUCTIONAL
15 PROGRAMS.
